text: Ernest Augustus I, Duke of Saxe-Weimar (German: Ernst August I; 19 April 1688 19 January 1748) was a duke of Saxe-Weimar. In 1741, he became the duke of Saxe-Weimar-Eisenach. Category:1688 births Category:1748 deaths Category:German dukes and duchesses Category:People from Weimar
title: Ernest Augustus I, Duke of Saxe-Weimar-Eisenach
